{"tid":178379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片)【名家搶先睇】給無殻蝸牛的忠告（利世民）","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T05:24:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aeba0d651068a4726771e9fe5046f7ed7905d44e","tid":178379,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170329/large/1490755372_0cc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170329%2Flarge%2F1490755372_0cc9.jpg&h=9e8b853b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增影片】最近跟一些比我後生十多年的朋友，談到置業的問題，他們當中有的是2005至2007年才出道工作，不少都任職於證券相關行業。過去十多年間，他們最有可能上車的日子，就應該是2008至2010年。可是，當時他們大多未儲得到首期。再者，自從2007年的港股大時代，證券市場其實沒有出現過真正的牛市，搵錢的也只限少數在 small cap 市場炒作的投機者。相對泛濫的資金流入樓市，他們這一群雖然在財經市場打滾，但無殻蝸牛卻佔了絕大多數，當中也有不少人至今仍然與家人同住。<br />\n<br />\n經濟週期，不但影響了一代人的資產配置，也在一定程度上改變了他們的價值觀。這些八十後財經市場從業員，雖然在價值觀上已經算是相對樂觀和保守，但他們也切身地感受到資產泡沫下的分配不均，或多或少也會希望目前的情況會出現轉機。<br />\n當然，他們也明白到，要政府作出干預，最終只會適得其反。所謂增加單位供應量的措施，也只會促成更多超微單位的出現。至於辣招，則增加易手樓成本，趕退炒家也只是令到市場流動性縮減，貨源歸邊。過去幾年政府對住宅市場的干預，結果就是令到不少新業主持有了超微單位。正如股市在泡沫最後階段，散戶手上持有的股票，不少都是沒有往續的新興企業。通常在泡沫爆破後，大家才發覺這些公司的市場狹窄，發展空間有限。<br />\n對各位無殻蝸牛，我的忠告是：「家庭七年的總收入，大約就是你可以負擔的樓價。假如覺得你可以負擔的選擇，不足以讓你住上十年或以上，目前最好還是持盈保泰，畢竟未來總有機會。」<br />\n利世民<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170329/56494399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170329%2F56494399&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=ee076825\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170329%2F56494399&h=e8e1c76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170329/56494399</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"73b343ca51dc10e2a2cecaaf0c98ce8549613a5f","tid":178379,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfceba5e86245e71a919abe2bd02ca9b6ac95968","tid":178379,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"兩萬一呎已經好普遍 過多兩年要四萬一呎"},{"pid":"c881e05000b13172e058363a0268ef1a32c2e047","tid":178379,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩萬一呎已經好普遍 過多兩年要四萬一呎</blockquote><br />\n宜家唔買,十萬蚊1尺時棺材都無得你訓"},{"pid":"d930c5974f94510e9cc30cd2807a8f9ed97a82db","tid":178379,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩萬一呎已經好普遍 過多兩年要四萬一呎</blockquote><br />\n記得前幾次 升到1萬蚊呎<br />\n個個都話痴撚線 好撚貴<br />\n宜家1萬蚊呎 個個都話好平仆曬去買"},{"pid":"a5b3eea31535ac57fe8d98f069a9d5953a150d1c","tid":178379,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"條link失效去呢條<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56494399&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56494399%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170329&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=eb2ec7bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56494399%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170329&h=10ab330f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56494399&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170329</a>"},{"pid":"aa3bb4e50b3bbdfe1c9c2991fc29e65370a66e79","tid":178379,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e80adac59bd25815ab03ee52fa53cf86b4ea683","tid":178379,"uid":60404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201